| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6610 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 91bdd1b9-884e-5282-9d03-16cf68f502da"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
